Image Prompt:
"Create an ethereal and majestic scene depicting a radiant figure surrounded by a halo of light, standing atop a mountain peak with a crown of thorns at their feet. The figure exudes humility and divine authority, with hands outstretched in a gesture of love and compassion. The landscape below is bathed in golden light, symbolizing spiritual enlightenment and the triumph of grace over earthly challenges. This image captures the essence of Jesus as the name above all names, embodying both humanity and divinity in perfect harmony."
